snippet.title: Mario Cars 2: 64 - Gameplay
snippet.description:
http://www.chelseasaunders.com/mariocars2

MC2: 64 was made in about a week by me (pixelatedcrown/Chelsea Saunders!) with help from KC Green (talking head art) and the Mario Cars 2 Tune Crew; Riki Tsuji, RJ Lake, Matt Martin and Vondell Swain. 

Download the OST here: https://mariocars.bandcamp.com
